---
// src/components/Testimonials.astro
---

<section id="depoimentos" class="py-32 md:py-48 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle background ambient -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[1000px] h-[1000px] bg-champagneGold/5 rounded-full blur-[150px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <!-- 1. DEPOIMENTOS (CAROUSEL) -->
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <div class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-champagneGold"></div>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-champagneGold font-bold">Prova Social</span>
        <div class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-champagneGold"></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white tracking-tighter">
        Vozes da <span class="italic text-champagneGold font-light">Transformação</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Carousel Container (Infinite Marquee) -->
    <div class="relative reveal delay-100 overflow-hidden w-full py-4 mask-edges">
      <div class="flex w-max animate-marquee hover-pause">
        
        <!-- SET 1 -->
        <div class="flex gap-6 pr-6">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="w-[85vw] md:w-[500px] shrink-0 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] p-10 flex flex-col justify-between backdrop-blur-md relative group hover:border-champagneGold/40 transition-colors duration-700 cursor-default">
            <span class="absolute top-8 right-8 iconify w-16 h-16 text-white/[0.03] group-hover:text-champagneGold/20 transition-colors duration-700 pointer-events-none" data-icon="lucide:quote"></span>
            <p class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-10 italic relative z-10">
              "Encontrar um espaço que una discrição absoluta e maestria técnica é raro. O Alexandre não apenas transforma, ele assina uma obra de arte respeitando quem somos. Um refúgio estético de alto padrão."
            </p>
            <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="iconify w-5 h-5 text-champagneGold" data-icon="lucide:user"></span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg tracking-wide">Isabella M.</h4>
                <span class="text-champagneGold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase font-mono mt-1 block">Empresária</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="w-[85vw] md:w-[500px] shrink-0 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] p-10 flex flex-col justify-between backdrop-blur-md relative group hover:border-champagneGold/40 transition-colors duration-700 cursor-default">
            <span class="absolute top-8 right-8 iconify w-16 h-16 text-white/[0.03] group-hover:text-champagneGold/20 transition-colors duration-700 pointer-events-none" data-icon="lucide:quote"></span>
            <p class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-10 italic relative z-10">
              "A primeira vez que estive no salão, percebi a diferença. O silêncio, a precisão cirúrgica e o nível de personalização me fizeram sentir única. A cor do meu cabelo nunca foi tão elogiada."
            </p>
            <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="iconify w-5 h-5 text-champagneGold" data-icon="lucide:user"></span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg tracking-wide">Victoria S.</h4>
                <span class="text-champagneGold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase font-mono mt-1 block">Arquiteta</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="w-[85vw] md:w-[500px] shrink-0 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] p-10 flex flex-col justify-between backdrop-blur-md relative group hover:border-champagneGold/40 transition-colors duration-700 cursor-default">
            <span class="absolute top-8 right-8 iconify w-16 h-16 text-white/[0.03] group-hover:text-champagneGold/20 transition-colors duration-700 pointer-events-none" data-icon="lucide:quote"></span>
            <p class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-10 italic relative z-10">
              "O que mais impressiona não é apenas a técnica inegável, mas o ritual de cuidado. É um ambiente onde a excelência é o padrão mínimo e a privacidade é levada a sério. Minha referência definitiva."
            </p>
            <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="iconify w-5 h-5 text-champagneGold" data-icon="lucide:user"></span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg tracking-wide">Helena B.</h4>
                <span class="text-champagneGold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase font-mono mt-1 block">Diretora de Arte</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 4 -->
          <div class="w-[85vw] md:w-[500px] shrink-0 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] p-10 flex flex-col justify-between backdrop-blur-md relative group hover:border-champagneGold/40 transition-colors duration-700 cursor-default">
            <span class="absolute top-8 right-8 iconify w-16 h-16 text-white/[0.03] group-hover:text-champagneGold/20 transition-colors duration-700 pointer-events-none" data-icon="lucide:quote"></span>
            <p class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-10 italic relative z-10">
              "A confiança que sinto ao entregar meus cabelos ao Alexandre é absoluta. O resultado é sempre sofisticado, com um cuidado impecável que vai além da estética e prioriza a saúde."
            </p>
            <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="iconify w-5 h-5 text-champagneGold" data-icon="lucide:user"></span>
